name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Whoa whoa wh-what the hell hell hell?

name: Agent
line: It's a monster!

name: Rick
line: What the hell are you doing, Morty?

name: Agent
line: We have to get out of here!

name: Rick
line: We got to get the hell out of there!

name: Agent
line: Get the hell away from here! We got to go.

name: Rick
line: Where are you guys going?

name: Agent
line: I don't know yet. I'll make it up as I go. That's what Grandpa Rick does. That is what heroes do.

name: Rick
line: Y-You want some privacy? I got some of that syringe F.D.'ing you up. Y-You got some that's gonna help too.

name: Agent
line: You're gonna need it later, Morty.

name: Rick
line: That's enough.

name: Agent
line: All right, well, let's do it.

name: Rick
line: I'll-I'll try to remember to shut off the brainalyzer.

name: Agent
line: Shut it off, Rick! You're not gonna help me with this!

name: Rick
line: Shut the fuck up!

name: Agent
line: Hey, it's fine. You're just being obstinate.

name: Rick
line: Not an issue, Rick.

name: Agent
line: Oh, I'm not an animal. You just keep crawling on my stuff like that.

name: Rick
line: It doesn't feel so good, does it?

name: Agent
line: Yeah, it does.
